{"tid":89281,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[齊抵制]一人一間串撫柒柒[出名]食店","createTime":"2017-01-21T08:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T10:41:22.000Z","uid":75299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75e21e1707d5da3cacb92ae35b13fbd439a3e59a","tid":89281,"uid":75299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\n[九記牛腩]個個伙記都柒撚碌碌食雞粥, 串到用個屎眼睇客, 又逼夾, 又唔撚係好食, 得個肥字, 仲要排隊, 真係唔撚明"},{"pid":"7bdf5893f02677c03d12c8ca497db6226a094110","tid":89281,"uid":45027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:36:26.000Z","msg":"住附近都唔會去食"},{"pid":"cc5d2f9072c2550d004dba096b62c6d3bc155ea3","tid":89281,"uid":16354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:00:17.000Z","msg":"澳牛"},{"pid":"982109c7f0aefb638802fd3868d7c9ff6c92cbd6","tid":89281,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:44:13.000Z","msg":"北海道，D嘢難食，人又閪口閪面"},{"pid":"f4dd527244a6780b7136993c592b5256fcdf5253","tid":89281,"uid":7453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我先<br />\n<br />\n[九記牛腩]個個伙記都柒撚碌碌食雞粥, 串到用個屎眼睇客, 又逼夾, 又唔撚係好食, 得個肥字, 仲要排隊, 真係唔撚明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n九記真係好普通 去對面食茄牛通好過<br />\n如果牛腩麵黎講 西營盤英記好食過佢"},{"pid":"ca42208a90da9575f0f69233995fe56d247a5c0e","tid":89281,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:32:16.000Z","msg":"九記其實唔差 一定係平均之上<br />\n<br />\n但太多遊客同好撚貴<br />\n<br />\n盡可能都唔會食"},{"pid":"6a8b2189d1498f22d2e755c5569172c2fef53c54","tid":89281,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>九記其實唔差 一定係平均之上<br />\n<br />\n但太多遊客同好撚貴<br />\n<br />\n盡可能都唔會食</blockquote><br />\n加冰糖煲到死爛嘅牛腩邊道好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cadd90ce684acf7450cad567dd0f7d7ca79c1a7","tid":89281,"uid":49481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:39:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳牛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前行過想食但聽講態度差到仆街就算了"},{"pid":"fae680f8dfcea4f7b369327cf0de8d2a9dafdda6","tid":89281,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:51:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>澳牛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前行過想食但聽講態度差到仆街就算了</blockquote><br />\n用華星一樣，算OK，聽人講依家態度好咗"},{"pid":"9623fb98e32f98f5ac2c5cdcd40556cdbfe82d5c","tid":89281,"uid":7453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:01:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳牛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過有伙記叫我慢慢飲 唔洗急 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effa9f9fd08a7cbf34a938d15d350b60540a4c68","tid":89281,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>九記其實唔差 一定係平均之上<br />\n<br />\n但太多遊客同好撚貴<br />\n<br />\n盡可能都唔會食</blockquote><br />\n你食開屎？"},{"pid":"d650ca76c1838aac29013a4fb0ad64a7293cad83","tid":89281,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T10:41:22.000Z","msg":"西環坤記煲仔小菜<br />\n<br />\n上至老細下至伙記都串過馬撚<br />\n唔知間野係咪𡃁坤開　<br />\n所以一脈相承咁撚黑人憎"}]}